title: Donovan Mitchell Blockbuster
description:
Adrian Wojnarowski breaks down the behind-the-scenes of the Cleveland Cavaliers’ blockbuster trade to acquire Utah’s Donovan Mitchell, including how the Knicks fell short in completing a trade on Monday.
